<div class="wrap">
<section class="install reveal" id="installation" style="margin:0 -48px">
  <div class="s-head">
    <div class="s-tag" style="color:var(--sage)">NO PLUMBER. NO TOOLS FROM THE GARAGE.</div>
    <h2 class="s-title">Installs in Under 5 Minutes</h2>
    <p class="s-sub">Thousands of women who've never done a home project installed this on the first try. Everything you need is in the box.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="install-grid">
    <div class="install-step"><div class="install-num">1</div><div class="install-icon">🔧</div><h4>Unscrew Your Old Head</h4><p>Turn it counter-clockwise by hand. No cutting, no drilling, no special tools.</p><span class="install-time">~2 min</span><div class="install-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div></div>
    <div class="install-step"><div class="install-num">2</div><div class="install-icon">🚿</div><h4>Attach Your ShowerEnvy</h4><p>Hand-tighten onto your shower arm. The rubber gasket creates a watertight seal. Filter is pre-installed.</p><span class="install-time">~2 min</span><div class="install-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div></div>
    <div class="install-step"><div class="install-num">3</div><div class="install-icon">💧</div><h4>Run &amp; Test</h4><p>Run water for 30 seconds. Use the included test strip — most women are shocked by the difference.</p><span class="install-time">~1 min</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="install-timer"><b>&lt; 5 min</b><p>Total install time · No plumber · No extra tools needed</p></div>
  <div class="install-trust">
    <div class="install-trust-item"><div class="install-trust-icon">🔌</div><span>Standard ½″ fitting — every U.S. shower arm</span></div>
    <div class="install-trust-item"><div class="install-trust-icon">📦</div><span>Rubber gasket seal — no tools needed</span></div>
    <div class="install-trust-item"><div class="install-trust-icon">🏠</div><span>Renter-friendly — take it when you move</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="install-compare">
    <div style="border:1.5px solid var(--sage)"><div class="ic-tag" style="color:var(--sage)">2.0 HANDHELD</div><h4>Same Ease + Hose Setup</h4><p>Screw on the head, click the 60″ hose onto the bracket. One extra connection — still under 5 minutes.</p></div>
    <div style="border:1.5px solid var(--gold)"><div class="ic-tag" style="color:var(--gold)">5.0 STATIONARY</div><h4>The Simplest Install</h4><p>Unscrew, screw on, done. Wall-mount fixed head. The 15-stage filter is fully pre-assembled. A 3-minute job.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>
</div>

